INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“All music is folk music. I ain’t never heard a horse sing a song.” ― Louis Armstrong');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I’m sick to death of people saying we’ve made 11 albums that sound exactly the same. In fact, we’ve made 12 albums that sound exactly the same.” ― Angus Young (AC/DC)');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“All the good music has already been written by people with wigs and stuff.” ― Frank Zappa');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“My music is best understood by children and animals.” ― Igor Stravinsky');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Do it again on the next verse, and people think you meant it.” ― Chet Atkins');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“To achieve great things, two things are needed: a plan and not quite enough time.” ― Leonard Bernstein');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“If I didn’t do this well, I just wouldn’t have anything to do…I can’t cook, and I’d be a terrible housewife.” ― Freddie Mercury (Queen)');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I don’t know anything about music, In my line you don’t have to.” ― Elvis Presley');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“There are two golden rules for an orchestra: start together and finish together. The public doesn’t give a damn what goes on in between.” ― Thomas Beecham');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“There are two kinds of artists left: those who endorse Pepsi and those who simply won’t.” ― Annie Lennox');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I’ve been imitated so well I’ve heard people copy my mistakes.” ― Jimi Hendrix');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“After I saw Jimmy [Hendrix] play, I just went home and wondered what the f*** I was going to do with my life.” ― Jeff Beck');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Money doesn’t talk, it swears.” ― Bob Dylan, Music at Night and Other Essays');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Actually I don’t remember being born, it must have happened during one of my black outs.” ― Jim Morrison');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I don’t deserve a Songwriters Hall of Fame Award. But fifteen years ago, I had a brain operation and I didn’t deserve that, either. So I’ll keep it!” ― Quincy Jones');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“When people say you’re doing something radical in rock or dance music, I’m not sure how special that is. What we do is so old-fashioned. It’s like trying to do something innovative in tap-dancing.” ― Jonny Greenwood (Radiohead)');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Competitions are for horses, not artists.” ― Bela Bartok');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I’d rather be a musician than a rock star.” ― George Harrison');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I smash guitars because I like them.” ― Pete Townshend');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“It’s easy to play any musical instrument: all you have to do is touch the right key at the right time and the instrument will play itself.” ― Johann Sebastian Bach');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Jazz is not dead, it just smells funny.” ― Frank Zappa');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I never had much interest in the piano until I realized that every time I played, a girl would appear on the piano bench to my left and another to my right.” ― Duke Ellington');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“There’s nothing like the eureka moment of knocking off a song that didn’t exist before – I won’t compare it to sex, but it lasts longer.” ― Paul McCartney');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Let me be clear about this: I don’t have a drug problem, I have a police problem.” ― Keith Richards');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I can’t understand why people are frightened of new ideas. I’m frightened of the old ones.” ― John Cage');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“When I was a little boy, I told my dad, ‘When I grow up, I want to be a musician.’ My dad said: ‘You can’t do both, Son’.” ― Chet Atkins');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“If you’re listening to a rock star to get your information on who to vote for, you’re a bigger moron than they are.” ― Alice Cooper');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“To listen is an effort, and just to hear is no merit. A duck hears also.” ― Igor Stravinsky');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“To get your playing more forceful, hit the drums harder.” ― Keith Moon (The Who)');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Sometimes we pee on each other before we go on stage.” ― Trent Reznor');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Dogs smoke in France.” ― Ozzy Osbourne');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“In order to compose, all you need to do is remember a tune that nobody else has thought of.” ― Robert Schumann');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I think John would have liked Free As A Bird. In fact, I hope somebody does this to all my crap demos when I’m dead, making them into hit songs.” ― George Harrison');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“In the end we’re all Jerry Springer Show guests, really, we just haven’t been on the show.” ― Marilyn Manson');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“If I knew I had to play this song the rest of my life I probably woulda wrote something else….” ― Joe Walsh (“Rocky Mountain Way”)');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Rock journalism is people who can’t write interviewing people who can’t talk in order to provide articles for people who can’t read.” ― Frank Zappa');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Too many pieces of music finish too long after the end.” ― Igor Stravinsky');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“I never practice my guitar… from time to time I just open the case and throw in a piece of raw meat.” ― Wes Montgomery');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“Lesser artists borrow, great artists steal.” ― Igor Stravinsky');
INSERT INTO QUOTE(quote) VALUES('“When an instrument fails on stage it mocks you and must be destroyed!” ― Trent Reznor');
